name: lulu in wonderland (5)
description:
This 5th lulu series might be a bit stressful, because after lulu finished the ramen boss, he had to deal with the hotdog boss..
lulu sees a little bun in peanut butter, and it turns out to be a cute cat, a cat made of peanut butter? sounds really delicious, but lulu wants him to be an adventure partner, evil is the right name for peanut butter, umm lulu means cute cat. why did the hotdog boss imprison the little cat in the jar? I don't know, maybe because he's a dog
